These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different games are played: chess, go, poker, whist
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing poker##1
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Game   | poker | go | chess | whist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
House: modern, art-deco, cottage, palace
1. the palace house is on the far right##1
2. the modern house is on the far left##1
3. the cottage house is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| House   | modern | cottage | art-deco | palace |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
House: tower, cape-cod, art-deco, gothic-revival
1. the art-deco house is on the left of the tower house##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| House   | art-deco | tower | cape-cod | gothic-revival |

