1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Sport   | biathlon | volleyball | lacrosse | skiing |

