.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, september, february, january
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |   3    |     4     |
| Birthday   | january | february | september | march |

